<P>
TURKISH BUS CRASH KILLS 11 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
ANKARA, Turkey 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Eleven people were killed and 26 injured when a bus plunged into a ditch on 
Wednesday near Gurun, 250 miles southeast of Ankara, the Anatolian News Agency 
reported. 
</P>
</TEXT>
