ROGER; HILLMAN, CHRIS; CROSBY, DAVID; CLARKE, MICHAEL; CLARK, GENE 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA010589-0157 </DOCNO>
