lead the Anteaters (5-1) at Heritage Park. Judd won the 200-meter freestyle in 
1 minute 46.85 seconds and the 500 freestyle in 4:50.82. Ro won the 200 
individual medley in 2:03.91 and the 200 breaststroke in 2:15.64. 
</P>
