In women's swimming: 
</P>
<P>
Danielle Pajar won two events as UC Irvine split a tri-meet with Fresno State 
and Northern Arizona. The Anteaters (3-4) defeated Northern Arizona, 151-92, 
but lost to Fresno State, 103-102. Pajar, a freshman, won the 200 freestyle in 
1:58.23 and the 200 breaststroke in 2:22.46. 
