Newport Harbor 69, Orange 41 -- Chris Lee scored 27 points to lead the Sailors 
(10-4) at Orange. Newport Harbor led, 18-8, at the end of the first quarter 
and, 30-16, at halftime. John Emigh scored 10 points for the Panthers (2-9). 
</P>
