<P>
Photo, Kindergartners from Rolling Hills Elementary School in Fullerton hike 
through the Oak Canyon Nature Center in Anaheim Hills. ; Photo, A 2 1/2-foot 
Rosy Boa found at Oak Canyon Nature Center. GAIL FISHER / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
